==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|y}}
===Etymology===
From the same Finno-Ugric *''ikte'' as Estonian [[üks]]
===Cardinal number===
'''yksi'''

#[[one]]

===Indefinite pronoun===
'''yksi'''

#[[one]], [[a]]

====Usage notes====
Traditionally, ''yksi'' has been used for "truly indefinite" things and ''[[eräs]]'' for things that the speaker knows but the listener not.

